author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Black-Eyed Snakes, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2018.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Walkin’ Talkin’ Blues
00:05:17 Alright Boys
00:08:02 Losing Water

Musicians
Alan Sparhawk — vocals, guitar
Bryan Johnson – percussion
Bob Olson — guitar
Brad Nelson — percussion

Credits
Engineer – Mike DeMark
Producer – Jesse Wiza
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
